metadata.title: Results of the Population Studies of Walleye Pollock (Theragra chalcogramma) in the Bering Sea. In: Proceedings of the International Scientific Symposium on the Bering Sea Fisheries. NOAA Tech. Memo. NMFS F/NWC-163:216-230
metadata.description: Anolyn's of morphemetric and merits features of pollock from the region of Bering Sea (donut hole and South eastern shelf). Materials were collected on board of fish vessels between Jan and March 1987.
